## ğŸ” Insights Generated

- T-Shirts contribute the highest revenue among all categories
- Medium and Large sizes account for the majority of sales volume
- Amazon-fulfilled orders dominate over merchant-fulfilled orders
- Metro and Tier-1 cities (Bengaluru, Mumbai, Delhi) generate maximum revenue
- Order cancellations remain under control with a low cancellation rate

---

## ğŸš€ How to Use This Project

1. Download the **Power BI (.pbix)** file from the repository  
2. Open it in **Microsoft Power BI Desktop**  
3. Use slicers to filter by category, date, fulfillment type  
4. Explore insights across different dashboard pages  
5. Modify or extend the dashboard using your own dataset  

